➜在高原戈壁观测浩瀚宇宙
http://www.sohu.com/a/427945668_267106	44934
<p><img src="//p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201028/6b51365920af43e3b5da731a67d7d0a6.jpeg" /></p>
